#: includes/sample-data.php:238
#: includes/sample-data.php:1582
msgid "Shadow Detective"
msgstr "影の探偵"

#: includes/sample-data.php:239
msgid "A full-fledged mystery game. Investigate the disappearance of businessman Makoto Kurosaki and uncover the truth. Gather evidence and make the right choices to reach the complete solution ending."
msgstr "本格的なミステリーゲーム。実業家・黒崎誠の失踪を調査し、真実を明らかにします。証拠を集め、正しい選択をして完全解決エンディングを目指しましょう。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:241
msgid "Investigation Failed"
msgstr "捜査失敗"

#: includes/sample-data.php:251
msgid "Shadow Detective - The Beginning"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 事件の始まり"

#: includes/sample-data.php:256
#: includes/sample-data.php:301
#: includes/sample-data.php:347
#: includes/sample-data.php:395
#: includes/sample-data.php:452
#: includes/sample-data.php:498
#: includes/sample-data.php:545
#: includes/sample-data.php:583
#: includes/sample-data.php:627
#: includes/sample-data.php:693
#: includes/sample-data.php:741
#: includes/sample-data.php:785
#: includes/sample-data.php:826
#: includes/sample-data.php:883
#: includes/sample-data.php:927
#: includes/sample-data.php:968
#: includes/sample-data.php:1010
#: includes/sample-data.php:1052
#: includes/sample-data.php:1099
#: includes/sample-data.php:1137
#: includes/sample-data.php:1217
#: includes/sample-data.php:1242
msgid "Detective"
msgstr "探偵"

#: includes/sample-data.php:258
#: includes/sample-data.php:303
#: includes/sample-data.php:450
#: includes/sample-data.php:691
#: includes/sample-data.php:1191
msgid "Misaki"
msgstr "美咲"

#: includes/sample-data.php:261
msgid "Detective, please help me... My husband has been missing for three days."
msgstr "探偵さん、お願いします...夫が3日前から行方不明なんです。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:262
msgid "The police say there's no criminal activity, but my husband would never do this..."
msgstr "警察は事件性はないと言いますが、夫は絶対にこんなことをする人ではありません..."

#: includes/sample-data.php:296
msgid "Shadow Detective - Details of Disappearance"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 失踪の詳細"

#: includes/sample-data.php:305
msgid "Three days ago in the evening, my husband said \"I have an important business meeting\" and left."
msgstr "3日前の夕方、夫は「重要な商談がある」と言って家を出ました。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:306
msgid "Since then, his phone hasn't connected, and he hasn't shown up at the company."
msgstr "それ以来、電話は繋がらず、会社にも姿を見せていません。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:307
msgid "Recently he seemed strange... as if he was worried about something."
msgstr "最近は様子が変で...何か悩んでいるようでした。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:321
msgid "First, I'll investigate the disappearance site"
msgstr "まずは失踪現場を調査します"

#: includes/sample-data.php:329
msgid "I'd like to hear from friends and acquaintances"
msgstr "友人・知人から話を聞きたい"

#: includes/sample-data.php:341
msgid "Shadow Detective - Warehouse District"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 港の倉庫街"

#: includes/sample-data.php:350
msgid "The warehouse district by the port where he was last seen. A deserted, dimly lit place."
msgstr "最後に目撃された港の倉庫街。人気のない薄暗い場所だ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:351
msgid "Something shiny is on the ground... It's a pocket watch."
msgstr "地面に何か光るものが落ちている...懐中時計だ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:352
msgid "Opening the back reveals an inscription: \"To Makoto, with love, Misaki\""
msgstr "裏蓋を開けると刻印がある：「誠へ 愛を込めて 美咲」"

#: includes/sample-data.php:353
msgid "This must belong to Makoto Kurosaki. Something happened here."
msgstr "これは黒崎誠のものに違いない。ここで何かがあったはずだ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:367
msgid "Return to the office to organize information"
msgstr "一旦事務所に戻って情報を整理する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:389
msgid "Shadow Detective - Time to Deduce"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 推理の時間"

#: includes/sample-data.php:398
msgid "Time to organize the gathered information."
msgstr "集めた情報を整理する時間だ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:399
msgid "The pocket watch... evidence he was at the disappearance site."
msgstr "懐中時計...これは失踪現場にいた証拠だ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:400
msgid "A businessman's sudden disappearance. Mention of family noticing strange behavior."
msgstr "実業家の突然の失踪。家族が奇妙な行動に気づいていたという言及。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:401
msgid "This case doesn't seem superficial."
msgstr "この事件、表面的なものではない気がする。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:412
msgid "The pocket watch found at the scene... and sudden disappearance. This connects to something bigger."
msgstr "現場で見つかった懐中時計…そして突然の失踪。これはもっと大きな何かに繋がっている。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:417
msgid "Prioritize questioning the family"
msgstr "家族への聞き込みを優先する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:425
msgid "Investigate friends and associates"
msgstr "友人・関係者を調査する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:445
msgid "Shadow Detective - Family Testimony"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 家族の証言"

#: includes/sample-data.php:455
msgid "He seemed to have problems with business partners... but he wouldn't tell me details."
msgstr "取引先との問題があったようですが……詳しいことは教えてくれませんでした。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:456
msgid "Also... there were calls from unknown men."
msgstr "あと...見知らぬ男性から電話がかかってくることもありました。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:457
msgid "My husband said \"It's fine\" but his expression was dark..."
msgstr "夫は「大丈夫だ」と言っていましたが、表情は暗かった..."

#: includes/sample-data.php:463
msgid "Talk to company associates"
msgstr "会社関係者に話を聞く"

#: includes/sample-data.php:471
msgid "Let me investigate the study"
msgstr "書斎を調査させてもらう"

#: includes/sample-data.php:475
msgid "Ask about the unknown callers in detail"
msgstr "見知らぬ電話の相手について詳しく聞く"

#: includes/sample-data.php:493
msgid "Shadow Detective - Friend's Testimony"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 友人の証言"

#: includes/sample-data.php:500
msgid "Sato"
msgstr "佐藤"

#: includes/sample-data.php:502
msgid "Mr. Makoto has been acting strange recently."
msgstr "誠さん、最近おかしかったんです。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:503
msgid "Last week, I happened to see him... talking with suspicious men."
msgstr "先週、偶然見かけたんですが...怪しい男たちと話していて。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:504
msgid "I was worried, so I took a photo. Here it is."
msgstr "心配になって写真を撮っておきました。これです。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:511
msgid "Investigate these men"
msgstr "この男たちについて調べる"

#: includes/sample-data.php:520
msgid "First, investigate the Kurosaki residence more"
msgstr "まずは黒崎邸をもっと調査する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:539
msgid "Shadow Detective - Secret of the Study"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 書斎の秘密"

#: includes/sample-data.php:548
msgid "With permission, I investigate the study."
msgstr "許可を得て書斎を調査する。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:549
msgid "Desk drawers contain receipts and contracts... nothing particularly suspicious."
msgstr "机の引き出しには領収書や契約書類……特に怪しいものはない。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:550
msgid "However, the bookshelf arrangement seems unnatural..."
msgstr "しかし、本棚の配置が不自然だ..."

#: includes/sample-data.php:551
msgid "Moving the bookshelf reveals... a hidden door!"
msgstr "本棚を動かすと...隠し扉！"

#: includes/sample-data.php:557
msgid "Try to open the hidden door"
msgstr "隠し扉を開けてみる"

#: includes/sample-data.php:561
#: includes/sample-data.php:802
msgid "Retreat for now"
msgstr "いったん引き返す"

#: includes/sample-data.php:565
msgid "Search the study more thoroughly first"
msgstr "まずは書斎をもっと徹底的に調べる"

#: includes/sample-data.php:577
msgid "Shadow Detective - Hidden Truth"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 隠された真実"

#: includes/sample-data.php:586
msgid "Beyond the hidden door is a small room. There's a safe and a desk."
msgstr "隠し扉の先は小さな部屋。金庫と机がある。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:587
msgid "A diary on the desk... It's Makoto Kurosaki's handwriting."
msgstr "机の上に手記が...黒崎誠の筆跡だ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:588
msgid "\"I chose the wrong path...\""
msgstr "「私は間違った道を選んでしまった...」"

#: includes/sample-data.php:589
msgid "\"I can't repay the debt to them. I don't want to trouble my family.\""
msgstr "「彼らからの借金を返せない。家族に迷惑をかけたくない。」"

#: includes/sample-data.php:595
msgid "Try to open the safe"
msgstr "金庫を開けてみる"

#: includes/sample-data.php:603
msgid "Take the diary back for analysis"
msgstr "手記を持ち帰って分析する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:621
msgid "Shadow Detective - To the Core of the Case"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 事件の核心へ"

#: includes/sample-data.php:631
msgid "The men in the photo from my friend... loan sharks?"
msgstr "友人からもらった写真の男たち...金貸しか？"

#: includes/sample-data.php:633
msgid "I need to find the key to the safe."
msgstr "金庫を開ける鍵を探さなければ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:644
msgid "The men in the photo from my friend... clearly loan sharks from Ryu-gumi."
msgstr "友人からもらった写真の男たち...金貸しか？"

#: includes/sample-data.php:652
msgid "The hidden room I found... There's definitely something big he was hiding."
msgstr "しかし、なぜ隠し部屋を？何か隠しているものがあるはずだ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:657
msgid "Ask the wife about the safe key"
msgstr "妻に金庫の鍵について聞く"

#: includes/sample-data.php:665
msgid "Pursue the men in the photo"
msgstr "友人の写真の男たちを追う"

#: includes/sample-data.php:686
msgid "Shadow Detective - Finding the Key"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 鍵の発見"

#: includes/sample-data.php:695
msgid "The safe key... Oh, I think there was a spare in my husband's study drawer."
msgstr "金庫の鍵……ああ、確か書斎の引き出しに予備があったと思います。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:698
msgid "This key might open the safe in the hidden room."
msgstr "この鍵で隠し部屋の金庫を開けられるかもしれない。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:704
msgid "Open the safe in the hidden room immediately"
msgstr "すぐに隠し部屋の金庫を開ける"

#: includes/sample-data.php:712
msgid "Gather other clues first"
msgstr "その前に他の手がかりも集める"

#: includes/sample-data.php:736
msgid "Shadow Detective - Dangerous Investigation"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 危険な調査"

#: includes/sample-data.php:743
msgid "Informant"
msgstr "情報屋"

#: includes/sample-data.php:746
msgid "Ah, these guys... dangerous bunch."
msgstr "ああ、この連中...ヤバい筋だぜ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:747
msgid "They're from \"Ryu-gumi\", a loan shark operation. Once you're in, you're done."
msgstr "「龍組」って闇金業者だよ。一度関わったら終わりさ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:748
msgid "Makoto Kurosaki? Yeah, I've heard. He owed them a huge amount."
msgstr "黒崎誠？聞いたことあるな...相当な額を借りてたらしいぜ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:754
msgid "Investigate Ryu-gumi in detail"
msgstr "龍組について詳しく調べる"

#: includes/sample-data.php:762
msgid "Search for more connections to Ryu-gumi"
msgstr "龍組との繋がりをさらに探る"

#: includes/sample-data.php:780
msgid "Shadow Detective - Dragon's Den"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 龍の巣窟"

#: includes/sample-data.php:787
msgid "Ryu-gumi Executive"
msgstr "龍組幹部"

#: includes/sample-data.php:789
msgid "Makoto Kurosaki? Yeah, I know him."
msgstr "黒崎誠のことか？ああ、知ってるよ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:790
msgid "He ran away after defaulting on a 30 million yen debt."
msgstr "3,000万の借金を踏み倒して逃げやがった。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:791
msgid "But we didn't do anything. You got no proof, right?"
msgstr "だが、俺たちは何もしちゃいねえ。証拠もないだろ？"

#: includes/sample-data.php:798
msgid "Press hard"
msgstr "強く追及する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:806
msgid "Try a different approach and negotiate"
msgstr "別のアプローチで交渉してみる"

#: includes/sample-data.php:820
msgid "Shadow Detective - Decisive Evidence"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 決定的証拠"

#: includes/sample-data.php:829
msgid "I use the key to open the safe."
msgstr "鍵を使って金庫を開ける。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:830
msgid "Inside are numerous documents and... cash!"
msgstr "中には大量の書類と...現金！"

#: includes/sample-data.php:843
msgid "And a name other than Ryu-gumi... \"Takagi Construction, President Takagi\"?"
msgstr "龍組以外の名前も……「高木建設　代表　高木」？"

#: includes/sample-data.php:848
msgid "Investigate Takagi Construction"
msgstr "高木建設について調べる"

#: includes/sample-data.php:857
msgid "Contact Ryu-gumi again"
msgstr "龍組にもう一度接触する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:877
msgid "Shadow Detective - Shadow of the Mastermind"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 黒幕の影"

#: includes/sample-data.php:886
msgid "Takagi Construction... a major general contractor. Why involved in illicit deals?"
msgstr "高木建設……大手ゼネコンだ。なぜ不正取引に関わっている？"

#: includes/sample-data.php:888
msgid "\"Payment from Kurosaki confirmed. Process next through Ryu-gumi\""
msgstr "「黒崎から入金確認。次は龍組経由で処理」"

#: includes/sample-data.php:895
msgid "Go directly to meet President Takagi"
msgstr "高木社長に直接会いに行く"

#: includes/sample-data.php:899
msgid "Gather more evidence"
msgstr "証拠をもっと集める"

#: includes/sample-data.php:921
msgid "Shadow Detective - Deepening Investigation"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 調査の深化"

#: includes/sample-data.php:930
msgid "Evidence has been accumulating. But I still don't have complete certainty."
msgstr "証拠は揃いつつある。だが、まだ確証が持てない。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:931
msgid "President Takagi's memo... this could be the decisive evidence."
msgstr "高木社長のメモ...これが決定的証拠になる。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:932
msgid "Ryu-gumi, Kurosaki, and Takagi Construction... the connections are becoming clear."
msgstr "龍組、黒崎、そして高木建設……繋がりが見えてきた。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:939
msgid "Interrogate President Takagi"
msgstr "高木社長を問い詰める"

#: includes/sample-data.php:943
msgid "Consult with the police"
msgstr "警察に相談する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:947
msgid "Verify the evidence one more time"
msgstr "証拠をもう一度検証する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:963
msgid "Shadow Detective - Encounter with the Mastermind"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 黒幕との邂逅"

#: includes/sample-data.php:970
#: includes/sample-data.php:1012
#: includes/sample-data.php:1054
#: includes/sample-data.php:1101
msgid "President Takagi"
msgstr "高木社長"

#: includes/sample-data.php:972
msgid "Detective, what brings you here?"
msgstr "探偵さん、何の用ですか？"

#: includes/sample-data.php:974
msgid "Please tell me about your relationship with Makoto Kurosaki."
msgstr "黒崎誠との関係について教えてください。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:975
msgid "Ah, I had a business relationship with him."
msgstr "ああ、彼とは仕事上の付き合いがありましたね。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:981
msgid "Explain this illicit transaction memo"
msgstr "この闇取引メモについて説明してください"

#: includes/sample-data.php:989
msgid "What about your relationship with Ryu-gumi?"
msgstr "龍組との関係は？"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1005
msgid "Shadow Detective - Cautious Approach"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 慎重な攻め"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1014
msgid "Ryu-gumi? Ah, I've heard rumors, but I have no connection with them."
msgstr "龍組？ああ、噂は聞いていますが、私は関係ありません。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1016
msgid "Detective, baseless defamation is libel, you know."
msgstr "探偵さん、根拠のない中傷は名誉毀損ですよ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1023
msgid "Wait, please look at this evidence"
msgstr "待ってください、この証拠を見てください"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1031
msgid "Sorry, excuse me"
msgstr "すみません、失礼しました"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1035
msgid "Try bluffing with partial evidence"
msgstr "部分的な証拠で揺さぶりをかける"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1047
msgid "Shadow Detective - Revealing the Truth"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 真実の暴露"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1057
msgid "...This is..."
msgstr "...これは..."

#: includes/sample-data.php:1059
msgid "Tch... Kurosaki left evidence behind."
msgstr "ちっ...黒崎のやつ、証拠を残していたのか。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1072
msgid "Where is Makoto Kurosaki?"
msgstr "黒崎誠はどこですか？"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1080
msgid "Tell me everything you know"
msgstr "知っていることをすべて話してください"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1094
msgid "Shadow Detective - All the Truth"
msgstr "影の探偵 - すべての真実"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1103
msgid "Fine... I'll tell you everything."
msgstr "わかった...すべて話そう。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1104
msgid "Kurosaki discovered my fraud. So I tried to silence him..."
msgstr "黒崎は私の不正を知ってしまった。それで口封じを..."

#: includes/sample-data.php:1105
msgid "But I didn't kill him. I asked Ryu-gumi to threaten him."
msgstr "だが、殺してはいない。龍組に頼んで脅したんだ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1112
msgid "Protect Kurosaki immediately"
msgstr "すぐに黒崎を保護する"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1120
msgid "Get the villa location first"
msgstr "まず別荘の場所を聞き出す"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1132
msgid "Shadow Detective - Reunion with the Missing"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 失踪者との再会"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1139
msgid "Makoto Kurosaki"
msgstr "黒崎誠"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1141
msgid "You're the detective..."
msgstr "あなたが探偵の..."

#: includes/sample-data.php:1142
msgid "I discovered Takagi's fraud and was threatened."
msgstr "私は高木の不正を知り、脅されていました。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1143
msgid "I was told my family would be harmed, so I had no choice but to hide."
msgstr "家族に危害が及ぶと言われ、隠れるしかなかった。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1157
msgid "Everything is resolved. Let's go back to your family"
msgstr "すべて解決しました。家族のもとへ帰りましょう"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1186
msgid "Shadow Detective - Complete Solution"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 完全解決"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1193
msgid "Makoto"
msgstr "誠"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1195
msgid "All evidence gathered, the truth has been revealed."
msgstr "すべての証拠を集め、真相を解明した。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1196
msgid "Detective, thank you so much."
msgstr "探偵さん、本当にありがとうございました。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1197
msgid "President Takagi was arrested, and I will cooperate with the police."
msgstr "高木社長は逮捕され、私も警察に協力することになりました。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1204
msgid "Complete Solution - All truths have been revealed"
msgstr "完全解決 - すべての真実が明らかになった"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1211
msgid "Shadow Detective - Partial Solution"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 部分解決"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1220
msgid "Makoto Kurosaki was protected, and the case saw some resolution."
msgstr "黒崎誠を保護し、事件は一応の解決を見た。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1221
msgid "However, I couldn't gather all the evidence."
msgstr "しかし、すべての証拠を集められなかった。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1222
msgid "President Takagi's crimes couldn't be fully proven, leaving parts unresolved."
msgstr "高木社長の罪を完全には証明できず、一部が未解決のまま終わった。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1229
msgid "Partial Solution - Some truths remain in darkness"
msgstr "部分解決 - 真相の一部は闇の中に"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1236
msgid "Shadow Detective - Insufficient Evidence"
msgstr "影の探偵 - 証拠不足"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1245
msgid "Evidence was insufficient, couldn't reach the truth."
msgstr "証拠が不十分で、真相に辿り着けなかった。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1246
msgid "Makoto Kurosaki remains missing."
msgstr "黒崎誠は今も行方不明のままだ。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1247
msgid "I should have been more careful and thorough in my investigation."
msgstr "もっと慎重に、丁寧に調査すべきだった。"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1254
msgid "Insufficient Evidence - Detective Failure"
msgstr "証拠不足 - 探偵失格"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1263
msgid "Pocket Watch"
msgstr "懐中時計"

#: includes/sample-data.php:1264
msgid "A pocket watch belonging to Makoto Kurosaki. Evidence he was at the disappearance site."
